data.description: Welcome to this 3,989 sq ft exquisite home in the desirable community of Rock Springs Estates located in Apopka, FL. This spacious 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, 1 half bath, 3 car garage, paved driveway, sparkling private pool offers a fully functional livable space and plenty of room for entertaining. Upon entering, awaits a formal living room or potential office space, family room includes a fireplace adjoining kitchen which includes granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, wine cellar, over-sized walk-in pantry. Upstairs you'll find all bedrooms including the primary suite and bathroom. A huge loft area for entertaining and gaming, right next door a theater room, California style walk-in closet, along with extra storage closet space throughout. As you make your way out back, you'll have plenty of time to enjoy Florida's sun and your very own enclosed lanai and paved pool deck, lots of yard space all fenced in for your very own privacy. Motivated to sell!! 32 miles from the Orlando Intl Airport, Central FL theme parks Disney & Universal Studios, shopping and dining and so much more! This home has it all! Let's turn this house into your dream home, schedule your showing today!
